<span id="freeTextContainer16757999163742297427">Politicians are like hookers. You can&apos;t be one unless you can pretend to like people while you&apos;re fucking them. <br/><br/><br/>In summary the propaganda model works like this: Bullshit politician with biased information is seen as an expert. Expert gives bullshit to news organization to inform the public. News organization repeats bullshit with cute voices and opinions. We all become stupid, except Chomsky. He writes this book. You read it. Become depressed and kill yourself. <br/><br/>I don&apos;t think I can do a serious r</span>
  <span id="freeText16757999163742297427" style="display:none">Politicians are like hookers. You can't be one unless you can pretend to like people while you're fucking them. <br /><br /><br />In summary the propaganda model works like this: Bullshit politician with biased information is seen as an expert. Expert gives bullshit to news organization to inform the public. News organization repeats bullshit with cute voices and opinions. We all become stupid, except Chomsky. He writes this book. You read it. Become depressed and kill yourself. <br /><br />I don't think I can do a serious review on this book. <br /></span>
